<li>Welchman, Jennifer, 1995, <em>Dewey&rsquo;s Ethical Thought</em>,
Ithaca, NY: Cornell University Press.</li>

<li>Westbrook, Robert B., 1991, <em>John Dewey and American
Democracy</em>, Ithaca, NY: Cornell University Press.</li>
</ul>
</div> 

